Hibiscus (entertainer) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hibiscus_(entertainer) 0 Hibiscus (born George Edgerly Harris III; September 6, 1949 – May 6, 1982) was the founder of the psychedelic gay liberation theater collective known as the Cockettes in early 1970s San Francisco.
